# ocular-microbiome web site supporting files
  
## URL 

    https://ccb.jhu.edu/ocular-microbiome/

## Build (using Sphinx)

    pip install sphinx
 
    git clone https://github.com/dpuiu/ocular-microbiome.git
 
    cd ocular-microbiome
    make html

## Config Files

    conf.py
    _static/custom.css

## reStructured text files

    index.rst
    Consortium.rst
    Research.rst
    Data_Access.rst
    footer.rst

## Image files

    _static/*.{png,jpg,jpeg}
